{"tid":1979460,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"13歲就識賣假CPU賺錢?","createTime":"2020-04-19T12:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T21:47:15.000Z","uid":104804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"315515b57aa25f23d96c981487af3f76c5b138d5","tid":1979460,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:18:03.000Z","msg":"定係背後有人操控<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n法籍男兩度網購CPU受騙 警拘2本地男童<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1964072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1964072</a><br />\n<br />\n警方於上月23日接獲一名37歲法國籍男子報案，指於3月4日在一個網上平台以1,600元購買一個中央處理器(CPU)，並相約賣家3月10日在中環港鐵站交收。事主回家後發現該中央處理器未能正常運作。他其後在3月21日以1,700元向同一賣家購買另一個中央處理器，並相約賣家3月23日於港鐵中環站交收。報案人在交收時發現該中央處理器為舊貨，懷疑受騙報警。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/19255/%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9C%9F_IHS_%E6%AE%BC%E5%81%87_U_%E5%AF%84_RMA_INTEL_%3A_%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E7%AF%A1%E6%94%B9%E6%A8%99%E8%AD%98%E6%8B%86_Die_%E9%A8%99%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F19255%2F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259C%259F_IHS_%25E6%25AE%25BC%25E5%2581%2587_U_%25E5%25AF%2584_RMA_INTEL_%253A_%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E7%25AF%25A1%25E6%2594%25B9%25E6%25A8%2599%25E8%25AD%2598%25E6%258B%2586_Die_%25E9%25A8%2599%25E6%25A1%2588&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=842e81ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/19255/%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9C%9F_IHS_%E6%AE%BC%E5%81%87_U_%E5%AF%84_RMA_INTEL_%3A_%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E7%AF%A1%E6%94%B9%E6%A8%99%E8%AD%98%E6%8B%86_Die_%E9%A8%99%E6%A1%88</a><br />\n【來自中國】真 IHS 殼、假 U 寄 RMA<br />\nINTEL : 出現大量篡改標識、拆 Die 騙案<br />\n<br />\n「假 U」事件在近年頻頻出現，騙徙多數會出沒在內地的網上商店如「鹹魚」，而大多數被換蓋的「假 U」都是 Intel 的處理器，例如有內地奸商在 AliExpress 阿里巴巴網上購物平台拿了個 400 顆的 Pentium G5400 處理器，開蓋把頂蓋換成了 Core i7-7700K 的頂蓋，並當作 7700K 來賣。當然在外國亦有混入不少的奸商，去年有位西班牙網友在 Amazon 不小心買到了假的 Core i9-9900K，但實質是 Core 2 Duo 處理器，另外亦有 Reddit 用戶稱買到假的 Core i7-8700K，結果是一個 Celeron 處理器，也是直接從 Amazon 購買的。"},{"pid":"a13eb7c7ab062f05150dd35d434844dd49de0369","tid":1979460,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:22:41.000Z","msg":"去新高登買冇咁嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d303048072e3a86274d53eb9f9671c1505b96526","tid":1979460,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"要搵2 個一心賺快錢嘅無知13歲男童交收，應該唔難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25894570d5fb440074bc7194dcf34f8c1771f0e3","tid":1979460,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"全部都係intel <br />\n<br />\n不愧係理財產品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1137d1e5f7776843bc32401ea6725c3796e89c12","tid":1979460,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:27:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a1f76b588531b40eb904abc453fa47219fb4e65","tid":1979460,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25894570d5fb440074bc7194dcf34f8c1771f0e3","tid":1979460,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"全部都係intel <br />\n<br />\n不愧係理財產品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:08:58.000Z","msg":"二手INTEL仲好值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e42be338e45927812a53ed738954a6a096433e","tid":1979460,"uid":19450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"315515b57aa25f23d96c981487af3f76c5b138d5","tid":1979460,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:18:03.000Z","msg":"定係背後有人操控<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n法籍男兩度網購CPU受騙 警拘2本地男童<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG